00:00:52.070 --> 00:00:54.460 align:middle line:90%
So what got you to start it?

00:00:54.460 --> 00:00:57.060 align:middle line:84%
What is this-- I've
heard of this 10

00:00:57.060 --> 00:00:58.470 align:middle line:90%
seconds that change your life.

00:00:58.470 --> 00:00:59.750 align:middle line:90%
Is that right?

00:00:59.750 --> 00:01:01.870 align:middle line:10%
My book's called the
"10-Second Philosophy,"

00:01:01.870 --> 00:01:03.690 align:middle line:10%
which is really
a practical guide

00:01:03.690 --> 00:01:05.920 align:middle line:10%
to releasing your inner genius.

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:08.085 align:middle line:10%
It really starts
because I believe

00:01:08.085 --> 00:01:10.070 align:middle line:10%
that everyone has a
genius inside of them

00:01:10.070 --> 00:01:11.790 align:middle line:10%
which I call the true self.

00:01:11.790 --> 00:01:13.580 align:middle line:84%
And if you get the true
self into your life,

00:01:13.580 --> 00:01:16.170 align:middle line:84%
you'll appear like a
genius because there

00:01:16.170 --> 00:01:17.750 align:middle line:90%
is a genius inside all of us.

00:01:17.750 --> 00:01:21.390 align:middle line:84%
And it can take just seconds
to open up that genius

00:01:21.390 --> 00:01:23.780 align:middle line:90%
and then change your whole life.

00:01:23.780 --> 00:01:24.940 align:middle line:90%
Let's go into it.

00:01:24.940 --> 00:01:29.390 align:middle line:84%
Let's go into how to do that
because it's true like now

00:01:29.390 --> 00:01:32.160 align:middle line:84%
in life we don't have
much time to bring

00:01:32.160 --> 00:01:33.880 align:middle line:84%
that genius out and
have those answers

00:01:33.880 --> 00:01:35.890 align:middle line:90%
and make those decisions.

00:01:35.890 --> 00:01:38.335 align:middle line:84%
So how can we tap into
that really quickly.

00:01:38.335 --> 00:01:41.250 align:middle line:84%
Well, it started for me
going back eight years ago.

00:01:41.250 --> 00:01:43.480 align:middle line:84%
I was in my office
working late one night.

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:45.930 align:middle line:84%
And I had been working
for about 18 years

00:01:45.930 --> 00:01:48.630 align:middle line:84%
as a financial services
financial planner,

00:01:48.630 --> 00:01:50.730 align:middle line:84%
and effectively, I
had been failing.

00:01:50.730 --> 00:01:52.180 align:middle line:84%
For the agency
that I worked for,

00:01:52.180 --> 00:01:53.720 align:middle line:84%
I was always at the
bottom of the list

00:01:53.720 --> 00:01:56.240 align:middle line:84%
struggling after 18
years in the business

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:59.220 align:middle line:84%
just about making ends
meet, not doing very well.

00:01:59.220 --> 00:02:02.850 align:middle line:84%
And to be frank, after
18 years, I had no money.

00:02:02.850 --> 00:02:06.070 align:middle line:84%
I was broke, and I was
not quite depressed,

00:02:06.070 --> 00:02:08.759 align:middle line:84%
but I'd say I was
clinically unhappy.

00:02:08.759 --> 00:02:12.650 align:middle line:10%
So I was in the office one
night one evening at 9:30,

00:02:12.650 --> 00:02:14.940 align:middle line:10%
and this [INAUDIBLE] guy
came into the office.

00:02:14.940 --> 00:02:19.390 align:middle line:10%
And he just said to me,
Derek, time to lock up.

00:02:19.390 --> 00:02:22.770 align:middle line:84%
And I said, just give me 10 more
minutes, and he walked away,

00:02:22.770 --> 00:02:23.610 align:middle line:90%
and then he came back in.

00:02:23.610 --> 00:02:25.830 align:middle line:84%
And I said, just give
me two more minutes.

00:02:25.830 --> 00:02:28.340 align:middle line:84%
And then he just looked at me,
and he asked me a question.

00:02:28.340 --> 00:02:32.060 align:middle line:10%
And he said, Derek, what time
did you get in this morning?

00:02:32.060 --> 00:02:33.570 align:middle line:10%
I said, well, 8 o'clock.

00:02:33.570 --> 00:02:36.030 align:middle line:10%
And literally as
he walked away, I

00:02:36.030 --> 00:02:38.940 align:middle line:10%
stood then-- I had
a moment, which

00:02:38.940 --> 00:02:41.770 align:middle line:10%
is my first 10-second moment
because in those 10 seconds

00:02:41.770 --> 00:02:44.810 align:middle line:10%
I literally stopped
and went inside, really

00:02:44.810 --> 00:02:46.250 align:middle line:10%
went introspectively.

00:02:46.250 --> 00:02:49.250 align:middle line:84%
And what came out of me was,
you're not happy because you're

00:02:49.250 --> 00:02:50.430 align:middle line:90%
not who you really are.

00:02:50.430 --> 00:02:51.460 align:middle line:90%
And you can't be truly happy.

00:02:51.460 --> 00:02:52.610 align:middle line:90%
It's not you.

00:02:52.610 --> 00:02:54.960 align:middle line:10%
What also came out of me
was some revelations for me

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:57.830 align:middle line:10%
at the time, which is I have
been setting goals for 18

00:02:57.830 --> 00:03:00.860 align:middle line:10%
years, doing the goal thing, as
you've all been taught to do,

00:03:00.860 --> 00:03:01.810 align:middle line:10%
for 18 years.

00:03:01.810 --> 00:03:05.270 align:middle line:84%
And after years, I was still
broke, and I was still unhappy.

00:03:05.270 --> 00:03:07.710 align:middle line:10%
So what came out me was
to stop setting goals,

00:03:07.710 --> 00:03:10.970 align:middle line:10%
stop setting goals, and instead
start setting standards for how

00:03:10.970 --> 00:03:13.550 align:middle line:10%
to live your life by the day.

00:03:13.550 --> 00:03:14.820 align:middle line:10%
So I did that.

00:03:14.820 --> 00:03:17.980 align:middle line:10%
And just for clarification,
a goal of course

00:03:17.980 --> 00:03:20.490 align:middle line:10%
is something that you set
up for tomorrow, next week,

00:03:20.490 --> 00:03:23.510 align:middle line:10%
next month, next year,
20 years into the future.

00:03:23.510 --> 00:03:26.560 align:middle line:84%
And what I understood for
myself and then for the people

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:30.320 align:middle line:84%
is that we all attach some of
our happiness and contentment

00:03:30.320 --> 00:03:31.850 align:middle line:90%
to achieving of that goal.

00:03:31.850 --> 00:03:34.280 align:middle line:10%
So that happiness and
contentment stays in the future

00:03:34.280 --> 00:03:36.970 align:middle line:10%
with that goal, but most
goals are not achieved,

00:03:36.970 --> 00:03:38.380 align:middle line:10%
so people never
get the happiness

00:03:38.380 --> 00:03:40.580 align:middle line:10%
really in their lives.

00:03:40.580 --> 00:03:41.780 align:middle line:90%
A standard is different.

00:03:41.780 --> 00:03:45.960 align:middle line:84%
A standard says this is who
I'm going to be just for today.

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:47.330 align:middle line:90%
This is who I am today.

00:03:47.330 --> 00:03:50.270 align:middle line:84%
These are the basis,
the criteria, the rules,

00:03:50.270 --> 00:03:52.130 align:middle line:84%
the levels, and the
qualities that I'm

00:03:52.130 --> 00:03:54.090 align:middle line:90%
going to live by today.

00:03:54.090 --> 00:03:55.630 align:middle line:84%
And they don't come
from outside of you,

00:03:55.630 --> 00:03:57.320 align:middle line:90%
they come from inside of you.

00:03:57.320 --> 00:04:02.000 align:middle line:10%
So for me, a quality, a level,
a rule, a basis, a criteria

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:04.610 align:middle line:10%
is something that says, who
am I really on the inside?

00:04:04.610 --> 00:04:05.720 align:middle line:90%
Who's the person inside?

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:07.280 align:middle line:90%
What's my true self?

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:10.190 align:middle line:84%
And to listen to the standards,
the qualities, rules,

00:04:10.190 --> 00:04:12.540 align:middle line:84%
criterias, levels, and base
that come from that place

00:04:12.540 --> 00:04:14.920 align:middle line:84%
and commit to living up
to the standards just one

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:17.529 align:middle line:84%
day at a time just
for today just

00:04:17.529 --> 00:04:20.309 align:middle line:84%
until you hit your head
back on your pillow tonight,

00:04:20.309 --> 00:04:21.190 align:middle line:90%
and that's it.

00:04:21.190 --> 00:04:22.400 align:middle line:90%
And I think we can all do that.

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:26.860 align:middle line:84%
We can all be ourselves, be our
true self, just for one day.

00:04:26.860 --> 00:04:28.940 align:middle line:84%
But if you say to me do this
for the rest of your life

00:04:28.940 --> 00:04:31.970 align:middle line:84%
over a 20-year business plan
or a three-year goal, it's

00:04:31.970 --> 00:04:33.730 align:middle line:84%
difficult. I was going
to leaders and teachers

00:04:33.730 --> 00:04:35.980 align:middle line:84%
from them around the world
and have all had challenges

00:04:35.980 --> 00:04:37.660 align:middle line:90%
with goals themselves.

00:04:37.660 --> 00:04:40.450 align:middle line:84%
So what we do know is that goals
are challenging for everyone,

00:04:40.450 --> 00:04:44.220 align:middle line:84%
and most people can either
take it to another place

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:47.790 align:middle line:84%
if they set standards, and
goals sometimes just don't work.

00:04:47.790 --> 00:04:49.650 align:middle line:90%
So I know this is different.

00:04:49.650 --> 00:04:52.881 align:middle line:84%
I know it's controversial, but
actually it's changing lives

00:04:52.881 --> 00:04:54.830 align:middle line:84%
and so did mine.
So that night--

00:04:54.830 --> 00:04:57.280 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, let's bring
it back to your life

00:04:57.280 --> 00:05:01.370 align:middle line:10%
because it really helps
us because otherwise

00:05:01.370 --> 00:05:03.210 align:middle line:10%
I just heard a lot of things.

00:05:03.210 --> 00:05:06.030 align:middle line:84%
And then it's wonderful when
we can just reflect in here

00:05:06.030 --> 00:05:07.990 align:middle line:90%
how this is, yeah, wonderful.

00:05:07.990 --> 00:05:10.975 align:middle line:10%
I mean really
simply, the place I

00:05:10.975 --> 00:05:13.690 align:middle line:10%
was in just going back
just over seven years ago

00:05:13.690 --> 00:05:14.970 align:middle line:10%
where I wasn't
seeing my children.

00:05:14.970 --> 00:05:16.770 align:middle line:10%
I was married.
I have four children.

00:05:16.770 --> 00:05:18.590 align:middle line:10%
I wasn't seeing them.
I was always working.

00:05:18.590 --> 00:05:20.120 align:middle line:10%
I wasn't seeing my wife.

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:21.550 align:middle line:84%
It was affecting
our relationships

00:05:21.550 --> 00:05:23.670 align:middle line:90%
with my wife and my children.

00:05:23.670 --> 00:05:26.800 align:middle line:10%
I wasn't happy in the office,
unhappy with people driving all

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:29.450 align:middle line:10%
over the country to see
people who didn't have

00:05:29.450 --> 00:05:32.360 align:middle line:10%
much money for
financial planning

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:34.230 align:middle line:10%
and really just going
wherever they said set up.

00:05:34.230 --> 00:05:36.030 align:middle line:84%
If they asked me to go to
the north or the south,

00:05:36.030 --> 00:05:39.240 align:middle line:84%
I would go, anytime,
anyplace, anywhere.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:41.160 align:middle line:84%
The problem with that
was I was so desperate

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:42.840 align:middle line:84%
and happy and
actually really just

00:05:42.840 --> 00:05:45.250 align:middle line:90%
struggling to have any success.

00:05:45.250 --> 00:05:50.130 align:middle line:10%
So after my change,
my epiphany-- that's

00:05:50.130 --> 00:05:52.360 align:middle line:10%
even if I want to call
it that-- literally,

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:53.980 align:middle line:10%
everything changed for
me because I changed.

00:05:53.980 --> 00:05:56.100 align:middle line:10%
I set standards,
and that evening

00:05:56.100 --> 00:05:59.085 align:middle line:10%
what I did I from inside I wrote
out some new standards to how

00:05:59.085 --> 00:06:00.690 align:middle line:10%
I was going to be as a person.

00:06:00.690 --> 00:06:02.620 align:middle line:84%
Because what did you
reply to that guy.

00:06:02.620 --> 00:06:04.490 align:middle line:84%
Oh, my reply to him
was actually nothing.

00:06:04.490 --> 00:06:05.560 align:middle line:90%
But he was already walking away.

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:09.080 align:middle line:84%
When I was in my moment, he
was already walking away.

00:06:09.080 --> 00:06:12.620 align:middle line:84%
But that phrase, that
question, just went inside.

00:06:12.620 --> 00:06:17.400 align:middle line:84%
Because to me, all of us
have moments that pass us by.

00:06:17.400 --> 00:06:20.240 align:middle line:84%
And maybe my moment
took me about 10 seconds

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:22.930 align:middle line:84%
to have someone ask me a
question and have me go inside

00:06:22.930 --> 00:06:24.810 align:middle line:84%
and answer that
question honestly

00:06:24.810 --> 00:06:26.460 align:middle line:90%
perhaps for the first time.

00:06:26.460 --> 00:06:28.360 align:middle line:90%
And that question changed me.

00:06:28.360 --> 00:06:30.830 align:middle line:84%
So I believe that any word,
thought, question, phrase,

00:06:30.830 --> 00:06:36.200 align:middle line:84%
or idea can change us if we
stop, pause, and allow it to go

00:06:36.200 --> 00:06:38.430 align:middle line:90%
inside and work inside of us.

00:06:38.430 --> 00:06:40.750 align:middle line:84%
So an idea that, and one
of the things that came out

00:06:40.750 --> 00:06:41.897 align:middle line:84%
was around standards,
and that was

00:06:41.897 --> 00:06:42.930 align:middle line:90%
what came out of my philosophy.

00:06:42.930 --> 00:06:45.770 align:middle line:84%
It was around standards, and
I set standards in my life

00:06:45.770 --> 00:06:47.000 align:middle line:90%
around the business.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:49.540 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't see any clients
below a certain wealth

00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:52.780 align:middle line:84%
because it was honoring them,
but it wasn't honoring me.

00:06:52.780 --> 00:06:54.360 align:middle line:84%
I wasn't doing
much money from it.

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:55.800 align:middle line:84%
There's no kind
of effect of that,

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:57.900 align:middle line:84%
so I wasn't seeing my
wife or my children.

00:06:57.900 --> 00:07:00.170 align:middle line:84%
So I set a minimum
criteria for clients

00:07:00.170 --> 00:07:02.850 align:middle line:90%
must have to be clients of mine.

00:07:02.850 --> 00:07:06.091 align:middle line:84%
I also decided no more six
days a week and no more

00:07:06.091 --> 00:07:06.790 align:middle line:90%
evening appointments.

00:07:06.790 --> 00:07:08.720 align:middle line:84%
So from a practical
point of view,

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:10.680 align:middle line:90%
I began to reclaim my life.

00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:13.820 align:middle line:84%
And the core standard was
around my family standards.

00:07:13.820 --> 00:07:17.080 align:middle line:84%
So taking my children to
school became my new standard

00:07:17.080 --> 00:07:18.110 align:middle line:90%
every single morning.

00:07:18.110 --> 00:07:19.920 align:middle line:10%
Picking my children
up from school three,

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:23.180 align:middle line:10%
four nights a week every single
week became another standard.

00:07:23.180 --> 00:07:26.700 align:middle line:84%
No more Fridays, no
Saturdays, half day Wednesday.

00:07:26.700 --> 00:07:29.150 align:middle line:84%
I even made a decision
around the people

00:07:29.150 --> 00:07:32.290 align:middle line:84%
I would work with as I was
advising that would have to be,

00:07:32.290 --> 00:07:35.040 align:middle line:84%
what I would call, nice people,
people I felt a connection

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:37.700 align:middle line:84%
with, because I wasn't
going to be in a place

00:07:37.700 --> 00:07:40.080 align:middle line:84%
where I would be seeing
people in my office,

00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:41.551 align:middle line:84%
but then still feeling
uncomfortable dealing

00:07:41.551 --> 00:07:42.250 align:middle line:90%
with them.

00:07:42.250 --> 00:07:44.200 align:middle line:84%
I made a decision that I would
deal with people I wanted

00:07:44.200 --> 00:07:45.655 align:middle line:84%
to deal with, who
I knew connected

00:07:45.655 --> 00:07:47.900 align:middle line:84%
with me, who I
connected with them,

00:07:47.900 --> 00:07:49.580 align:middle line:90%
and that they were nice people.

00:07:49.580 --> 00:07:51.300 align:middle line:84%
That sounds an
odd phrase to use,

00:07:51.300 --> 00:07:54.030 align:middle line:84%
but I've been messed around and
abused so much over the years

00:07:54.030 --> 00:07:55.960 align:middle line:90%
by clients, I made a decision.

00:07:55.960 --> 00:07:57.515 align:middle line:84%
All my clients must
be nice people.

00:07:57.515 --> 00:08:00.187 align:middle line:84%
I must want to work with them
and feel that connection.

00:08:00.187 --> 00:08:01.720 align:middle line:84%
And something else that
really changed my life

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:03.810 align:middle line:84%
was to make the decisions
that all clients

00:08:03.810 --> 00:08:06.310 align:middle line:84%
must come to my office no matter
where they were in the country.

00:08:06.310 --> 00:08:08.670 align:middle line:84%
They must come to me, so
made lots of standards

00:08:08.670 --> 00:08:13.310 align:middle line:84%
around my lifestyle and
who I was as a person,

00:08:13.310 --> 00:08:15.620 align:middle line:90%
and it just changed everything.

00:08:15.620 --> 00:08:18.220 align:middle line:84%
Quite literally change--
my relationships, obviously

00:08:18.220 --> 00:08:20.820 align:middle line:84%
my children, my wife,
they all improved.

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:21.970 align:middle line:90%
They all got better.

00:08:21.970 --> 00:08:24.790 align:middle line:84%
I felt better as a person
because I felt real.

00:08:24.790 --> 00:08:27.040 align:middle line:84%
I felt this is really
me living my life.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:29.880 align:middle line:84%
What I've noticed is up
until that point in my life

00:08:29.880 --> 00:08:33.490 align:middle line:84%
my standards were
set by the business,

00:08:33.490 --> 00:08:36.250 align:middle line:90%
the community, my clients.

00:08:36.250 --> 00:08:39.510 align:middle line:84%
Someone said 10 years ago,
the industry, the economy,

00:08:39.510 --> 00:08:41.559 align:middle line:84%
set by these different
areas that weren't me.

00:08:41.559 --> 00:08:42.940 align:middle line:84%
For the very first
time in my life

00:08:42.940 --> 00:08:46.840 align:middle line:84%
I started to stop and go
inside and set standards

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:48.560 align:middle line:84%
for who I really
was as a person,

00:08:48.560 --> 00:08:49.660 align:middle line:84%
and that made all
the difference.

00:08:49.660 --> 00:08:53.750 align:middle line:84%
So from that point onwards, my
life changed so dramatically.

00:08:53.750 --> 00:08:57.000 align:middle line:84%
People began to turn up
and say, what did you do?

00:08:57.000 --> 00:09:00.127 align:middle line:84%
Because you were doing this
bad for 18 years, and I

00:09:00.127 --> 00:09:02.480 align:middle line:84%
didn't quite.
I was famous for my persistence.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.445 align:middle line:90%
I wouldn't quit.

00:09:03.445 --> 00:09:05.730 align:middle line:84%
But how could you be so bad
for so long then suddenly

00:09:05.730 --> 00:09:07.950 align:middle line:84%
virtually overnight--
it's not an exaggeration--

00:09:07.950 --> 00:09:09.210 align:middle line:90%
overnight things changed?

00:09:09.210 --> 00:09:11.950 align:middle line:84%
And they changed overnight
because I changed.

00:09:11.950 --> 00:09:14.670 align:middle line:84%
Between those 10 seconds, I
became a different person.

00:09:14.670 --> 00:09:16.625 align:middle line:84%
Of course, it took time,
weeks and months and a couple

00:09:16.625 --> 00:09:18.910 align:middle line:84%
of years, to see the
results in the business,

00:09:18.910 --> 00:09:21.280 align:middle line:84%
but the result was
guaranteed because I changed.

00:09:21.280 --> 00:09:22.080 align:middle line:90%
Does that make sense?

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:24.330 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, but why did
it not happen before?

00:09:24.330 --> 00:09:26.680 align:middle line:84%
Because we all see
this, and there's

00:09:26.680 --> 00:09:28.620 align:middle line:84%
years and years and
years of sometimes

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:30.950 align:middle line:84%
procrastinating and
saying, [INAUDIBLE],

00:09:30.950 --> 00:09:32.660 align:middle line:90%
until there is a sudden event.

00:09:32.660 --> 00:09:35.190 align:middle line:10%
Or we get fired, or
there is a disease,

00:09:35.190 --> 00:09:37.130 align:middle line:10%
or there's something
really dramatic.

00:09:37.130 --> 00:09:41.810 align:middle line:84%
So why didn't you hear this
before or had this moment?

00:09:41.810 --> 00:09:44.030 align:middle line:90%
What does create such a moment?

00:09:44.030 --> 00:09:45.960 align:middle line:84%
I think what the
reality of it is

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:47.860 align:middle line:84%
I'd had plenty of
messages from the universe

00:09:47.860 --> 00:09:49.800 align:middle line:90%
to say, stop what you're doing.

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:51.820 align:middle line:84%
This isn't working
for you, and because I

00:09:51.820 --> 00:09:56.130 align:middle line:84%
was trapped in what I call
non-self, or in the world,

00:09:56.130 --> 00:09:57.380 align:middle line:90%
I ignored them.

00:09:57.380 --> 00:09:59.870 align:middle line:84%
I think we all do in life
have times and messages

00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:02.345 align:middle line:84%
that we pick up from the
universe, a word, a thought,

00:10:02.345 --> 00:10:03.910 align:middle line:84%
a question, [INAUDIBLE],
an incident,

00:10:03.910 --> 00:10:05.540 align:middle line:90%
and we do nothing with it.

00:10:05.540 --> 00:10:08.300 align:middle line:84%
We don't allow it to
work inside of us,

00:10:08.300 --> 00:10:10.370 align:middle line:84%
so we don't get the
change because I look back

00:10:10.370 --> 00:10:12.440 align:middle line:90%
and I had plenty of moments.

00:10:12.440 --> 00:10:14.480 align:middle line:10%
I tell you one
night I was actually

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:16.610 align:middle line:10%
driving back from a
client's late one night

00:10:16.610 --> 00:10:17.760 align:middle line:10%
and I driving my car.

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:20.005 align:middle line:10%
And it was probably about
10:00, 10:30 in the evening,

00:10:20.005 --> 00:10:22.080 align:middle line:10%
and all I wanted to do
was just to get home

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:24.860 align:middle line:10%
to see my wife before she went
to bed, maybe look at the kids

00:10:24.860 --> 00:10:25.680 align:middle line:10%
before I went to bed.

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:27.646 align:middle line:84%
Because I knew I wouldn't see
them the next morning because

00:10:27.646 --> 00:10:29.900 align:middle line:90%
be up before they were up.

00:10:29.900 --> 00:10:32.480 align:middle line:84%
So what actually happened
is I'm driving along,

00:10:32.480 --> 00:10:33.970 align:middle line:84%
and I'm looking at
the car in front.

00:10:33.970 --> 00:10:35.770 align:middle line:84%
And the car in front
is driving so slowly.

00:10:35.770 --> 00:10:39.320 align:middle line:84%
I'm thinking, why is he driving
so slowly, I need to get home.

00:10:39.320 --> 00:10:42.490 align:middle line:10%
So I put my foot
down to overtake him,

00:10:42.490 --> 00:10:45.350 align:middle line:10%
and it's only when I crashed
into the motorway barrier

00:10:45.350 --> 00:10:48.985 align:middle line:10%
and bounced back that I realized
I was already in the fast lane.

00:10:48.985 --> 00:10:50.820 align:middle line:84%
I was so tired I
didn't know I was

00:10:50.820 --> 00:10:52.540 align:middle line:90%
already in the overtaking lane.

00:10:52.540 --> 00:10:55.380 align:middle line:84%
And thank God there
wasn't a truck behind.

00:10:55.380 --> 00:10:57.010 align:middle line:84%
There wasn't anything
that, otherwise I wouldn't

00:10:57.010 --> 00:10:58.630 align:middle line:90%
be literally here today.

00:10:58.630 --> 00:11:01.700 align:middle line:84%
But I had lots of little signals
and a lot of big signals,

00:11:01.700 --> 00:11:04.140 align:middle line:84%
but I didn't really
pay attention to them.

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:06.610 align:middle line:10%
So what I realized was that
sometimes it just takes

00:11:06.610 --> 00:11:09.400 align:middle line:10%
a moment, or a word, or
a thought, or a question,

00:11:09.400 --> 00:11:13.270 align:middle line:10%
or a phrase, or an idea
just to get us to pause.

00:11:13.270 --> 00:11:16.310 align:middle line:84%
And thank God that
night in November, 2003,

00:11:16.310 --> 00:11:18.940 align:middle line:84%
I took that question from
an office security guard.

00:11:18.940 --> 00:11:20.360 align:middle line:90%
I call him my first coach.

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:22.480 align:middle line:84%
He doesn't know this
because the office

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:25.240 align:middle line:84%
suit guards change so often,
but he just asked a question.

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:27.590 align:middle line:84%
He was new to the building,
and I just said to him,

00:11:27.590 --> 00:11:29.380 align:middle line:90%
now give me some more time.

00:11:29.380 --> 00:11:32.060 align:middle line:84%
But when he asked that
question, it just made me stop.

00:11:32.060 --> 00:11:35.550 align:middle line:10%
And sometimes to find the
philosophy and the truth that's

00:11:35.550 --> 00:11:39.720 align:middle line:10%
inside of us, we've got to just
stop for a moment and pause

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:42.950 align:middle line:10%
and allow the phrase or
the question to sink in

00:11:42.950 --> 00:11:45.140 align:middle line:10%
and to see what comes
from that place.

00:11:45.140 --> 00:11:46.740 align:middle line:84%
So I don't know if
you want to know what

00:11:46.740 --> 00:11:48.150 align:middle line:90%
my life looked like after that?

00:11:48.150 --> 00:11:49.180 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:11:49.180 --> 00:11:49.920 align:middle line:90%
OK, so--

00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:51.340 align:middle line:84%
Right, and there's
a [INAUDIBLE]

00:11:51.340 --> 00:11:53.930 align:middle line:84%
OK, yeah, but basically I
don't know how relevant it is

00:11:53.930 --> 00:11:56.140 align:middle line:84%
because working as
a financial planner

00:11:56.140 --> 00:11:58.240 align:middle line:84%
and just paying your
bills each month

00:11:58.240 --> 00:12:00.250 align:middle line:84%
is not very inspirational
for your clients.

00:12:00.250 --> 00:12:01.250 align:middle line:90%
It's not good for you.

00:12:01.250 --> 00:12:03.240 align:middle line:84%
And your colleagues don't
think very highly of you.

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:04.810 align:middle line:84%
But I can tell you
is within three years

00:12:04.810 --> 00:12:06.410 align:middle line:84%
from that being broke and
just paying the bills,

00:12:06.410 --> 00:12:07.800 align:middle line:90%
I'm a millionaire.

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:09.495 align:middle line:84%
The following year, I
made a million dollars

00:12:09.495 --> 00:12:11.981 align:middle line:84%
in just that year, and I did
it working less than half

00:12:11.981 --> 00:12:13.620 align:middle line:84%
the time.
-It's a big change.

00:12:13.620 --> 00:12:17.670 align:middle line:84%
Yes, big change because it was
around saying, OK, standards.

00:12:17.670 --> 00:12:20.920 align:middle line:84%
It's as if when I set standards
that my truth began to speak

00:12:20.920 --> 00:12:22.720 align:middle line:84%
to the world because
what I can tell

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:26.400 align:middle line:84%
you is this is that the company
I worked for didn't change.

00:12:26.400 --> 00:12:28.070 align:middle line:90%
The products didn't change.

00:12:28.070 --> 00:12:30.790 align:middle line:84%
The presentation, the slides
were pretty much the same.

00:12:30.790 --> 00:12:31.660 align:middle line:90%
That didn't change.

00:12:31.660 --> 00:12:33.550 align:middle line:84%
About the hotel using
for presentations,

00:12:33.550 --> 00:12:34.730 align:middle line:90%
that didn't change either.

00:12:34.730 --> 00:12:40.800 align:middle line:10%
What changed was me, and what
I can't yet put into words even

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:43.310 align:middle line:10%
now, but I do fancy
that what was happening,

00:12:43.310 --> 00:12:46.160 align:middle line:10%
is when people were meeting
me, they were feeling me

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:47.860 align:middle line:10%
and seeing me differently.

00:12:47.860 --> 00:12:50.150 align:middle line:10%
And because they were picking up
on a different energy or aspect

00:12:50.150 --> 00:12:53.250 align:middle line:10%
of me unconsciously,
they were going,

00:12:53.250 --> 00:12:54.760 align:middle line:10%
I'll do business with him.

00:12:54.760 --> 00:12:56.140 align:middle line:90%
I'll connect with this person.

00:12:56.140 --> 00:12:57.930 align:middle line:90%
I'll introduce him to so-and-so.

00:12:57.930 --> 00:13:00.370 align:middle line:84%
These were essentially the
same people who, for 18 years,

00:13:00.370 --> 00:13:02.740 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't get a meeting with
or had a first meeting with.

00:13:02.740 --> 00:13:04.610 align:middle line:84%
I didn't get a
second meeting with.

00:13:04.610 --> 00:13:06.540 align:middle line:84%
So what essentially
happened is people turned up

00:13:06.540 --> 00:13:09.600 align:middle line:84%
in such great numbers
that I had to then ask

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:11.370 align:middle line:84%
other people in the
organization, other agents,

00:13:11.370 --> 00:13:13.710 align:middle line:84%
to help me to service
those clients.

00:13:13.710 --> 00:13:15.920 align:middle line:90%
Then something else happened.

00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:17.200 align:middle line:84%
Because the results
came, you know,

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:22.170 align:middle line:84%
living in the business world,
I had my first waking up, which

00:13:22.170 --> 00:13:24.140 align:middle line:90%
had occurred to me that night.

00:13:24.140 --> 00:13:26.690 align:middle line:84%
Other agents kept approaching
me and saying, Derek, we

00:13:26.690 --> 00:13:27.780 align:middle line:90%
now you're bad.

00:13:27.780 --> 00:13:29.387 align:middle line:84%
We know you're not
very good at this job,

00:13:29.387 --> 00:13:30.620 align:middle line:84%
but you're suddenly
turning your life

00:13:30.620 --> 00:13:32.890 align:middle line:84%
from being really, really
bad to exceptionally good,

00:13:32.890 --> 00:13:35.410 align:middle line:84%
one of the top 1%
in the UK and then

00:13:35.410 --> 00:13:37.730 align:middle line:90%
one of the top 1% in the world.

00:13:37.730 --> 00:13:39.770 align:middle line:90%
How did you do that?

00:13:39.770 --> 00:13:43.040 align:middle line:10%
Because I became a member
of the Top of the Table,

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:46.030 align:middle line:10%
which is the highest level of
the Million Dollar Round Table,

00:13:46.030 --> 00:13:47.570 align:middle line:10%
which is an organization
that represents

00:13:47.570 --> 00:13:49.990 align:middle line:10%
financial planners, financial
advisers, and wealth

00:13:49.990 --> 00:13:51.800 align:middle line:10%
managers around the world.

00:13:51.800 --> 00:13:53.800 align:middle line:84%
So what was interesting
is that they

00:13:53.800 --> 00:13:55.950 align:middle line:84%
kept turning up and saying,
well, what did you do?

00:13:55.950 --> 00:13:58.940 align:middle line:10%
And to be frank, when they first
turned up, I started saying,

00:13:58.940 --> 00:14:00.920 align:middle line:10%
well, I wasn't myself.

00:14:00.920 --> 00:14:01.790 align:middle line:90%
I found my true self.

00:14:01.790 --> 00:14:04.600 align:middle line:84%
I accessed all of that, and
I had the guts to be who

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:06.190 align:middle line:90%
I really was into the world.

00:14:06.190 --> 00:14:08.580 align:middle line:84%
Some of them got it,
but a lot of them

00:14:08.580 --> 00:14:11.680 align:middle line:84%
didn't get in because
they were the left

00:14:11.680 --> 00:14:13.840 align:middle line:84%
brain-conscious busy people.
Show me the number.

00:14:13.840 --> 00:14:15.400 align:middle line:90%
Show me the process.

00:14:15.400 --> 00:14:18.380 align:middle line:84%
But that's where my genius
came back into play because I

00:14:18.380 --> 00:14:20.647 align:middle line:84%
believe that every one of us
has a genius inside of a us,

00:14:20.647 --> 00:14:22.570 align:middle line:84%
and when we access it,
it gives us the answers.

00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:23.790 align:middle line:90%
It shows us the way.

00:14:23.790 --> 00:14:24.990 align:middle line:90%
It gives us the ideas.

00:14:24.990 --> 00:14:27.090 align:middle line:90%
It even gives us the words.

00:14:27.090 --> 00:14:31.225 align:middle line:84%
So I began to say,
OK, what this is

00:14:31.225 --> 00:14:32.310 align:middle line:90%
you know you're setting goals.

00:14:32.310 --> 00:14:34.043 align:middle line:84%
And you're here because
you're not really that happy

00:14:34.043 --> 00:14:37.260 align:middle line:84%
and you're not that
successful according to you.

00:14:37.260 --> 00:14:39.210 align:middle line:84%
I said that I stopped
setting goals.

00:14:39.210 --> 00:14:40.660 align:middle line:84%
What you need to do
is set standards.

00:14:40.660 --> 00:14:42.380 align:middle line:84%
Now to a left brain
business-conscious

00:14:42.380 --> 00:14:44.410 align:middle line:84%
person, that looks like,
oh, it's another process

00:14:44.410 --> 00:14:45.680 align:middle line:90%
like setting goals.

00:14:45.680 --> 00:14:47.160 align:middle line:84%
But in fact, it
wasn't because what

00:14:47.160 --> 00:14:51.070 align:middle line:84%
standards are is a thing that
comes from the inside of you.

00:14:51.070 --> 00:14:52.480 align:middle line:10%
So they started
setting standards,

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:54.730 align:middle line:10%
reviewing their old standards.

00:14:54.730 --> 00:14:56.310 align:middle line:10%
And setting new
standards, and to do

00:14:56.310 --> 00:14:59.660 align:middle line:10%
that, they had to go inside.

00:14:59.660 --> 00:15:02.210 align:middle line:84%
So it was really
like a miracle to me

00:15:02.210 --> 00:15:04.300 align:middle line:84%
to have people coming in looking
for process in the business

00:15:04.300 --> 00:15:05.984 align:middle line:84%
model, suddenly go
setting standards,

00:15:05.984 --> 00:15:07.250 align:middle line:84%
and so you don't do
get your standards

00:15:07.250 --> 00:15:09.550 align:middle line:84%
from the outside world,
that's why you're not happy.

00:15:09.550 --> 00:15:12.520 align:middle line:84%
That's why you haven't got
success that you desire.

00:15:12.520 --> 00:15:13.670 align:middle line:84%
You take a stance
from the inside

00:15:13.670 --> 00:15:15.510 align:middle line:90%
by an internal reference.

00:15:15.510 --> 00:15:18.260 align:middle line:84%
And as I did that, the
magic was having people

00:15:18.260 --> 00:15:21.020 align:middle line:84%
coming in for a
result on that process

00:15:21.020 --> 00:15:24.310 align:middle line:84%
and having them turn around
and go, here's how I feel.

00:15:24.310 --> 00:15:26.230 align:middle line:84%
This is really-- I
feel connected here.

00:15:26.230 --> 00:15:28.340 align:middle line:10%
And they talk about their
wife and their children

00:15:28.340 --> 00:15:30.740 align:middle line:10%
and their husband and
things [INAUDIBLE] feelings

00:15:30.740 --> 00:15:32.315 align:middle line:10%
with clients and having
a better connection

00:15:32.315 --> 00:15:34.680 align:middle line:10%
and feeling more honest
and more truthful.

00:15:34.680 --> 00:15:37.020 align:middle line:84%
And that clearly
was my resonance.

00:15:37.020 --> 00:15:38.540 align:middle line:90%
So it was a joy.

00:15:38.540 --> 00:15:41.890 align:middle line:10%
It was a revelation to me, sort
of the same thing that worked

00:15:41.890 --> 00:15:45.820 align:middle line:10%
for me, having standards
take people inside to access

00:15:45.820 --> 00:15:50.250 align:middle line:10%
their true self and to have the
guts to follow the advice that

00:15:50.250 --> 00:15:51.570 align:middle line:10%
came from true self.

00:15:51.570 --> 00:15:55.150 align:middle line:10%
Because what happens is that
when you access your true self,

00:15:55.150 --> 00:15:57.420 align:middle line:10%
the more access it,
the more it speaks to,

00:15:57.420 --> 00:15:59.430 align:middle line:10%
the more message it
gives you, the more truth

00:15:59.430 --> 00:16:00.420 align:middle line:10%
it reveals to you.

00:16:00.420 --> 00:16:02.580 align:middle line:10%
And it does that
through words, thoughts,

00:16:02.580 --> 00:16:06.920 align:middle line:10%
questions, phrases, and ideas
that come from within to share.

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:09.400 align:middle line:84%
So what is the
dialogue like, or how do

00:16:09.400 --> 00:16:11.070 align:middle line:90%
you formulate those standards?

00:16:11.070 --> 00:16:14.110 align:middle line:84%
How do you get in
there to get them out?

00:16:14.110 --> 00:16:15.810 align:middle line:10%
Actually, the funny thing
is the very first night,

00:16:15.810 --> 00:16:17.220 align:middle line:10%
it was completely accidental.

00:16:17.220 --> 00:16:19.250 align:middle line:10%
It was just a question
that called me.

00:16:19.250 --> 00:16:21.600 align:middle line:10%
Actually, it's a
question that caused me

00:16:21.600 --> 00:16:23.834 align:middle line:10%
almost like a mini meditation.

00:16:23.834 --> 00:16:25.500 align:middle line:10%
Because I remember in the
office when I was there,

00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:28.820 align:middle line:10%
and I literally just
stopped, and I paused

00:16:28.820 --> 00:16:33.360 align:middle line:10%
and feeling really, really
centered and really comfortable

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:35.140 align:middle line:10%
but knowing that
something tremendous

00:16:35.140 --> 00:16:36.870 align:middle line:10%
was going on inside of me.

00:16:36.870 --> 00:16:39.080 align:middle line:10%
But it was knowing
that my consciousness

00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:39.940 align:middle line:10%
was really within.

00:16:39.940 --> 00:16:42.150 align:middle line:10%
I was looking deeply
introspectively.

00:16:42.150 --> 00:16:44.260 align:middle line:10%
So even though I wouldn't have
called it that then-- I would

00:16:44.260 --> 00:16:45.630 align:middle line:10%
have just called
it a moment-- it

00:16:45.630 --> 00:16:48.290 align:middle line:10%
was like doing a
deep meditation,

00:16:48.290 --> 00:16:50.480 align:middle line:10%
instant meditation going
in for a few seconds

00:16:50.480 --> 00:16:52.000 align:middle line:10%
and holding that place.

00:16:52.000 --> 00:16:53.930 align:middle line:10%
And as I held that place.

00:16:53.930 --> 00:16:56.470 align:middle line:10%
What came up, I paid
attention to it.

