00:27:01.300 --> 00:27:04.240 align:middle line:84%
growing and developing
there and crying sometimes

00:27:04.240 --> 00:27:05.560 align:middle line:90%
and giggling sometimes.

00:27:05.560 --> 00:27:07.500 align:middle line:84%
But that's the real
you that's inside,

00:27:07.500 --> 00:27:08.920 align:middle line:84%
and if you had a
baby in your hands,

00:27:08.920 --> 00:27:10.410 align:middle line:90%
you'd nurture that wouldn't you.

00:27:10.410 --> 00:27:13.710 align:middle line:84%
And that's the real- you grow
