00:27:15.770 --> 00:27:18.180 align:middle line:90%
and inspirations and ideas.

00:27:18.180 --> 00:27:20.900 align:middle line:84%
And that changes your life
because when you change,

00:27:20.900 --> 00:27:23.160 align:middle line:84%
everything changes for you,
