00:27:23.160 --> 00:27:25.100 align:middle line:84%
you finding the
change inside of you

00:27:25.100 --> 00:27:28.260 align:middle line:90%
and all those things changing.

00:27:28.260 --> 00:27:30.560 align:middle line:84%
And often when people speak
about their inner child,

00:27:30.560 --> 00:27:34.040 align:middle line:84%
yes, they are there to nurture
that inner child because it

00:27:34.040 --> 00:27:36.140 align:middle line:90%
hasn't been really listened to.

00:27:36.140 --> 00:27:40.110 align:middle line:84%
All we did is absorb and
get all those publicity

00:27:40.110 --> 00:27:46.720 align:middle line:84%
and those advertisers and the
messages and kind of dream

00:27:46.720 --> 00:27:48.540 align:middle line:84%
like if it was our
dream, but it's not.

00:27:48.540 --> 00:27:51.760 align:middle line:84%
