00:28:01.630 --> 00:28:04.920 align:middle line:10%
but also has that oneness.

00:28:04.920 --> 00:28:07.960 align:middle line:84%
Every soul on the planet
is part of everything

00:28:07.960 --> 00:28:10.980 align:middle line:84%
as in we're all
connected together.

00:28:10.980 --> 00:28:15.420 align:middle line:84%
And I know that is a
common way of thinking

00:28:15.420 --> 00:28:17.030 align:middle line:84%
and believing for
those who are awake

00:28:17.030 --> 00:28:18.710 align:middle line:90%
or we might say enlightened.

00:28:18.710 --> 00:28:21.160 align:middle line:84%
I genuinely believe that
we're all connected together.

00:28:21.160 --> 00:28:23.550 align:middle line:84%
What I also believe is
that because of that,

00:28:23.550 --> 00:28:25.810 align:middle line:84%
because we're all part of the
