00:32:58.190 --> 00:33:00.470 align:middle line:10%
and to be guided by that
and to have the guts

00:33:00.470 --> 00:33:02.700 align:middle line:10%
and to have the courage
to be who you really

00:33:02.700 --> 00:33:05.650 align:middle line:10%
are because once
you shuffle off,

00:33:05.650 --> 00:33:07.980 align:middle line:10%
you can't be who you
are after you've gone.

00:33:07.980 --> 00:33:11.400 align:middle line:90%
It's about now and doing it now.

00:33:11.400 --> 00:33:12.950 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, Steve Job, whoa.

