I mean, what is your advice in
regards to that because I think

00:34:05.700 --> 00:34:09.070 align:middle line:84%
this is a strong example of
overcoming and just being

00:34:09.070 --> 00:34:13.440 align:middle line:84%
ourselves fully and owning
who we are in our magnificence

00:34:13.440 --> 00:34:16.270 align:middle line:84%
that we can all relate to that
whatever that challenge is.

00:34:16.270 --> 00:34:19.060 align:middle line:84%
But I guess, I
mean, that was huge.

00:34:19.060 --> 00:34:20.110 align:middle line:90%
Was it there for you?

00:34:20.110 --> 00:34:23.960 align:middle line:84%
Or you were actually brought in
this very nurturing, loving way

00:34:23.960 --> 00:34:25.690 align:middle line:84%
that you always knew
exactly your place,

00:34:25.690 --> 00:34:27.239 align:middle line:84%
or behind the back
of your mind it

00:34:27.239 --> 00:34:32.020 align:middle line:84%
was still there, that maybe you
didn't deserve to have this.

00:34:32.020 --> 00:34:35.219 align:middle line:84%
