a young boy I grew up.

00:34:35.219 --> 00:34:39.719 align:middle line:10%
And as young boy, I
loved my mother dearly.

00:34:39.719 --> 00:34:41.560 align:middle line:84%
And I was really
close to my mother,

00:34:41.560 --> 00:34:44.830 align:middle line:84%
and what was
interesting is that I

00:34:44.830 --> 00:34:46.440 align:middle line:84%
